flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens App]) --> Enter[Enter Text]
    Enter --> Validate{Valid?}
    
    Validate -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    Error --> Enter
    
    Validate -->|Yes| Translate[Translate to Victorian]
    Translate --> Success{Success?}
    
    Success -->|Yes| Display[Display Result]
    Display --> Actions{User Action?}
    Actions -->|Speak| Audio[Play Audio]
    Actions -->|Copy| Copy[Copy Text]
    Actions -->|New| Enter
    Actions -->|Done| End([Exit])
    
    Success -->|No| ErrorMsg[Show Error]
    ErrorMsg --> End
    
    Audio --> Actions
    Copy --> Actions

    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style Translate fill:#FFD700
